{
  "_comment": "hugr-lightr built-in `--seccomp default` curated profile. Default-deny (ERRNO/EPERM) allow-list, derived from the Docker/moby default seccomp profile, filtered to the x86_64 syscall names the WP-#111 compiler (crates/lightr-engine/src/engine/seccomp.rs `syscall_nr`) resolves. Pure uniform-ALLOW list, no `args` (the #111 compiler shape). DO NOT add `args`-conditioned entries or names absent from `syscall_nr` — both fail the compile closed.",
